#: salesforce_object_flow/pages/welcome.py:27
msgid ""
"Compose multi-object, transactional creates against the Salesforce REST "
"Composite API."
msgstr ""
"Compón creaciones multiobjeto y transaccionales contra la API REST "
"Composite de Salesforce."

